included.description:
Advised leading bank and insurance leadership teams (CFO, CRO) on core financial operational, strategic, and organizational issues. Developed and assessed financial forecast, valuation, and risk management models. 

Selected work:
- Led team of five consultants to assess internally developed insurance and pricing models for a large US financial firm. Identified major loss forecasting model shortcomings (hundreds of millions of dollars)
- Developed economic capital tool for large US health insurer using Monte Carlo simulation techniques. Led weekly sessions with senior working team and structured key interviews with various business unit heads.
- Assessed balance sheet management strategy for a top-3 US diversified bank using financial projection assessments.  Identified underperforming units and evaluated potential investment scenarios that were presented directly to the CFO.

included.description:
I led Coinbase's USDC team, working closely with Circle and Centre to create a trusted, global, dollar-based crypto currency. We jointly grew USDC—the world's largest, trusted USD-backed cryptocurrency stablecoin—to $40 BN market cap and growing. 

Under my leadership, the Coinbase team:
- Launched the USDC Bootstrap Fund with investments in Uniswap, Compound, dYdX, PoolTogether and more; DeFi summer was the first massive growth wave for USDC
- Pitched leading policy makers and regulators (e.g., the US Federal Reserve) on the benefits of Central Bank Digital Currencies (CBDC)
- Supported the integration of USDC into leading DeFi protocols like dYdX
- Grew the Centre Consortium with Circle
included.title: Senior Product Manager, USDC

included.description:
I led Coinbase's Crypto teams. Under my leadership, we:
- Doubled the number of assets on Coinbase's platform, adding Solana, Filecoin, Aave, Uniswap, and more
- Enabled key staking and DeFi rewards, including launching staking for Ethereum
- Launched Rosetta, a cross-blockchain API standard used by the world's leading blockchains (https://www.rosetta-api.org)
- Launched the Coinbase Community Fund, supporting foundational crypto open source development and research
- Developed tools to secure access and custody of $200 BN+ of funds
